      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's been such a joy to drive! It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me through every trip. If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks great and runs smoothly, this is definitely the one. I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it just as much as I have. Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
