    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 straight-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This unit delivers linear power delivery to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension maintain factory-spec kinematics. While the exterior shows minor evidence of spirited use, the powertrain is dialed in with recent valve adjustments and a cooling system overhaul. A true driver\u2019s example with exceptional longitudinal and lateral dynamics.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
