      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six. This high-revving power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. This example has had the critical 'Big Three' addressed: the rear subframe has been reinforced, rod bearings replaced with treated shells, and the VANOS system overhauled with uprated seals. The chassis remains composed thanks to a refreshed multi-link rear suspension and MacPherson strut front end, providing the communicative feedback these cars are known for. While the exterior shows the honest patina of a well-enjoyed machine, the mechanical synchronization and drivetrain integrity are excellent.",
